txt.en: You have collected enough spider venom.\n\nYou should give the phials to Kúlthrak at Kafagur.
Kúlthrak has asked you to hunt down spiders for venom.\n\nSpiders can be found at Maj Khibi, which is located north-west of Kafagur.
Collect venom from spiders at Maj Khibi ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Kúlthrak is in need of spider venom for wound-numbing purposes.

'I used up the last of my spider venom on Nargai. Their pain has dulled for now, but that won't last if I don't get my hands on more venom.\n\n'If you're up to the task, hunt down some spiders for me, yeah? There're plenty of them north-west of us at Maj Khibi.'
